mac system preferences
1.turn on darkmode
2. turn up mouse speed
3. look up how to enable repeating keys
4. sync chrome
5. ctrl-shift-h/l to go side to side
6. download backgrounds
7. setup pfp, import to photos
8. enable touchid
9. add keyboard shortcuts !check = checkemoji, use ctrl cmd space to emoji
10. Change caps to ctr;
11. disable dock
12. install magnet

vscode
1. copy vscode bindings
2. install material theme/icon
3. install python
3. install vim
4. turn on vscode sync

Setup terminal
- Download kitty terminal
	- set themes for kitty, with `kitten themes`
- install homebrew
- install helix editor
	- set themes for helix
	- cp -r ./src/dotfiles/helix ~/.config/helix
- Install inconsolata powerline font
	- https://github.com/powerline/fonts
- copy zshrc from dotfiles
- install spaceship prompt
- install oh my zsh

brew install zsh-syntax-highlighting



